      "title": "82 people hospitalised after yesterday\u2019s clashes",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The number of people injured during the clashes which erupted yesterday had increased to 84 and admitted to the Colombo National Hospital (CNH)",
        "Hospital sources said 42 were admitted yesterday during the clash near Parliament last night. (CS)"
